  "response_text": "A young girl stands centered on a small stage in front of dark blue curtains, facing a tall black microphone. She has light skin, long brown hair in two braids, large clear-framed glasses, and a neat school-uniform look: a white collared shirt under a red plaid jumper, with large dark blue bows near her shoulders. She looks composed and confident, with a slight smile, as if performing in a spelling bee or school recital. While speaking, she gestures delicately with one hand near the microphone, then raises both hands to adjust her glasses at the temples. Her expression stays calm and self-assured as she finishes, looking straight ahead.\n\nThe scene widens to reveal the stage more fully. An American flag stands on a pole at the left, blue curtains hang on both sides, and a square black mat or shadowed area lies on the wooden floor. Suddenly, an enormous gray cube descends into the center of the stage, filling the space where the girl had been. Its surface is mottled and metallic-looking, and a bright circular spotlight washes across its front face. The cube lands upright, massive and imposing, with the flag still visible beside it.\n\nThe visuals then switch into the video game world: a glossy, dark, grid-like platform floating in black space. Large blocks form a moving wall ahead, made of gray cubes mixed with solid black cubes and glowing green cubes. A tiny human-like character, wearing a pale top and yellowish pants, stands on the reflective floor beside highlighted squares that change color from blue to red. The character runs along the grid as the block formations advance.\n\nA wider view shows multiple rows of blocks sliding forward like a wave across a long tiled pathway. The green cubes glow with a watery neon texture, the black cubes look dangerous and opaque, and the gray cubes have a cloudy metal sheen. A small ESRB rating box marked “K-A” appears in the lower right during the gameplay shots.\n\nThe little game character navigates narrow spaces between towering cubes. In one moment, the character is hemmed in beside a high wall of blocks as a bright white block rises or flashes nearby, making the character appear very small against the massive cube surfaces. In another, the character runs along the edge of a stepped cube formation, close to glowing green blocks and a black cube set into the grid.\n\nAs the blocks continue to shift, the character loses footing near the edge of the platform. The figure tips backward with arms raised and falls away from the tiled surface into black emptiness. Several views show the character tumbling between huge floating gray cubes, limbs splayed, shrinking against the surrounding block structures.\n\nThe commercial returns to the stage. The giant gray cube now stands in the center under the circular spotlight, with mist or smoke drifting near its upper left edge. The American flag remains at the left, and the blue curtains frame the scene. Across the front face of the cube, black-and-white block lettering spells the game title: “Intelligent Qube.”",
